@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Which Maruti Suzuki S-Presso Variant Offers the Best Value?";
}
@section MetaTags {
    <meta name="keywords" content="S-Presso variants comparison, best S-Presso variant, S-Presso VXi+, S-Presso price in India, Maruti S-Presso value for money, budget car variants" />
    <meta name="description" content="Confused between S-Presso variants? Explore this detailed guide to find out which variant of the Maruti Suzuki S-Presso gives you the best features for your budget." />
}
<body id="bg">
    <div class="header-img"><img src="~/images/main-slider/header.png" alt="Header Image" /></div>
    <div class="blog-main-container">
        <div class="latest-bikes-details-content">
            <h3 class="subheading">Best Value-for-Money Variant of the Maruti Suzuki S-Presso</h3>
            <div class="row m-b20">
                <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 text-center"><img src="~/images/valueformoney/2025/may/marutispresso/banner.png" alt="banner" title="banner" /></div>
            </div>
            <p>Choosing the right variant of the S-Presso can make all the difference in terms of features, comfort, and price. Here’s a breakdown of each variant and which one offers the best value.</p>
            <div style="overflow-x: auto;">
                <table class="comparison-table-content">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th class="text-center"><span class="font-weight-600">Variant</span></th>
                            <th class="text-center"><span class="font-weight-600">Fuel Type</span></th>
                            <th class="text-center"><span class="font-weight-600">Transmission</span></th>
                            <th class="text-center"><span class="font-weight-600">On-Road Price (₹)</span></th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr class="compare-head-text">
                            <td>STD (O)</td>
                            <td>Petrol</td>
                            <td>Manual</td>
                            <td>₹4.73 lakh</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>LXi (O)</td>
                            <td>Petrol</td>
                            <td>Manual</td>
                            <td>₹5.51 lakh</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr class="compare-head-text">
                            <td>VXi (O)</td>
                            <td>Petrol</td>
                            <td>Manual</td>
                            <td>₹5.75 lakh</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>VXi Plus (O)</td>
                            <td>Petrol</td>
                            <td>Manual</td>
                            <td>₹6.06 lakh</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr class="compare-head-text">
                            <td>VXi (O) AGS</td>
                            <td>Petrol</td>
                            <td>Automatic (AMT</td>
                            <td>₹6.28 lakh</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>VXi Plus (O) AGS</td>
                            <td>Petrol</td>
                            <td>Automatic (AMT</td>
                            <td>₹6.77 lakh</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr class="compare-head-text">
                            <td>LXi (O) CNG</td>
                            <td>CNG</td>
                            <td>Manual</td>
                            <td>₹6.50 lakh</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>VXi (O) CNG</td>
                            <td>CNG</td>
                            <td>Manual</td>
                            <td>₹6.90 lakh</td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
            <h3 class="subheading">STD Variant (₹4.26 lakh)</h3>
            <div class="row m-b20">
                <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 text-center"><img src="~/images/valueformoney/2025/may/marutispresso/exterior4.webp" alt="exterior4" title="exterior4" /></div>
                <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 text-center"><img src="~/images/valueformoney/2025/may/marutispresso/exterior5.webp" alt="exterior5" title="exterior5" /></div>
            </div>
            <p><span class="font-weight-600">Pros:</span> Cheapest entry point</p>
            <p><span class="font-weight-600">Cons:</span> Lacks power steering, basic features only</p>
            <p><span class="font-weight-600">Best for:</span> Buyers on an extremely tight budget</p>
            <h3 class="subheading">LXi (₹4.95 lakh)</h3>
            <p><span class="font-weight-600">Adds:</span> Power steering, AC, dual airbags</p>
            <p><span class="font-weight-600">Best for: </span>Functional daily use, minimal frills</p>
            <h3 class="subheading">VXi / VXi+ (₹5.15–₹5.65 lakh)</h3>
            <p><span class="font-weight-600">Adds:</span></p>
            <div class="row m-b20">
                <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 text-center"><img src="~/images/valueformoney/2025/may/marutispresso/highlight1.webp" alt="highlight" title="highlight" /></div>
                <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 text-center"><img src="~/images/valueformoney/2025/may/marutispresso/highlight5.webp" alt="highlight" title="highlight" /></div>
            </div>
            <ul>
                <li>Front power windows</li>
                <li>SmartPlay Studio (VXi+)</li>
                <li>Electrically adjustable ORVMs</li>
                <li>Central locking</li>
            </ul>
            <p><span class="font-weight-600">Best for:</span> Most buyers looking for comfort and infotainment without overspending.</p>
            <h3 class="subheading"> Value-for-Money Verdict: VXi+ (Manual or AGS)</h3>
            <p>The <span class="font-weight-600">VXi+</span> strikes the perfect balance between price and features. It adds essential creature comforts, infotainment, and cosmetic upgrades that elevate the ownership experience without crossing the ₹6 lakh mark. If you want the convenience of automatic without spending much, the VXi+ AGS is the sweet spot.</p>
